## Warden Agent Guide

Use this as your fast orientation for the Warden macOS SwiftUI app. It tells you where key things live and how to implement common changes safely.

### Core Entry Points
- **Main app**: [Warden/WardenApp.swift](mdc:Warden/WardenApp.swift)
- **Root UI**: [Warden/UI/ContentView.swift](mdc:Warden/UI/ContentView.swift)
- **Configuration & model lists**: [Warden/Configuration/AppConstants.swift](mdc:Warden/Configuration/AppConstants.swift)
- **Data models**: [Warden/Models/Models.swift](mdc:Warden/Models/Models.swift), [Warden/Models/MessageContent.swift](mdc:Warden/Models/MessageContent.swift)
- **Persistence (Core Data)**: [Warden/Store/ChatStore.swift](mdc:Warden/Store/ChatStore.swift), [Warden/Store/warenDataModel.xcdatamodeld](mdc:Warden/Store/warenDataModel.xcdatamodeld)

### API Abstraction (Multi-Provider)
- **Unified protocol**: [Warden/Utilities/APIHandlers/APIProtocol.swift](mdc:Warden/Utilities/APIHandlers/APIProtocol.swift)
- **Handler factory**: [Warden/Utilities/APIHandlers/APIServiceFactory.swift](mdc:Warden/Utilities/APIHandlers/APIServiceFactory.swift)
- **High-level orchestrator**: [Warden/Utilities/APIServiceManager.swift](mdc:Warden/Utilities/APIServiceManager.swift)
- **Per-provider handlers**: see [Warden/Utilities/APIHandlers/](mdc:Warden/Utilities/APIHandlers/)
- **Message building/parsing**: [Warden/Utilities/MessageManager.swift](mdc:Warden/Utilities/MessageManager.swift), [Warden/Utilities/MessageParser.swift](mdc:Warden/Utilities/MessageParser.swift)
- **Request conversion**: [Warden/Models/RequestMessagesTransformer.swift](mdc:Warden/Models/RequestMessagesTransformer.swift)

### Reasoning Models (o1/o3/deepseek-reasoner, etc.)
- Warden supports special "thinking" streams and display.
- Convert system messages to user role for reasoning models.
- Show reasoning content in UI, separated from final content.
- UI: [Warden/UI/Chat/ThinkingProcessView.swift](mdc:Warden/UI/Chat/ThinkingProcessView.swift)
- Example handling (pattern):
```swift
// Example pattern used in reasoning-capable handlers
if let reasoningContent = message["reasoning_content"] as? String {
    finalContent = "<think>\n\(reasoningContent)\n</think>\n\n\(messageContent)"
}
```

